                        A complete platform for artists, collectors, and art enthusiasts.
                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="single-info row mt-40">

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 mt-120 text-center no-padding info-left">

                <div class="info-thumb">

                    <img src="~/User/img/pages/about-img.jpg"
                         class="img-fluid"
                         alt="About Art Gallery">

                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 no-padding info-rigth">

                <div class="info-content">

                    <h2 class="pb-30">

                        Discover<br>

                        Buy, Sell & Auction<br>

                        Amazing Artwork

                    </h2>

                    <p>

                        Our Art Gallery is designed to help artists showcase
                        their creativity and connect directly with buyers.
                        Whether you are a professional artist or just starting
                        your creative journey, our platform provides the tools
                        needed to display and sell your artwork.

                    </p>

                    <br>

                    <p>

                        Buyers can browse artworks from multiple categories,
                        view detailed information, save favorite items to
                        their wishlist, purchase securely, and monitor all
                        orders from their personal dashboard.

                    </p>

                    <br>

                    <p>

                        Our auction system creates a fair and exciting
                        environment where collectors compete for exclusive
                        artwork. When the bidding period ends, the highest
                        bidder becomes the winner automatically.

                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>



